Maintainer: Akiru Kato <paithiov909@gmail.com>
Description: R package based on 'Rcpp' for 'MeCab': Yet Another
    Part-of-Speech and Morphological Analyzer. The purpose of this package
    is providing a seamless developing and analyzing environment for CJK
    texts. This package utilizes parallel programming for providing highly
    efficient text preprocessing 'posParallel()' function.
